(14, 3, '7-Day Budget Adventure: Tokyo & Dubai from Vizag', 'Plan a 7 days budget trip for 4 friends starting from Visakhapatnam (Vizag), going first to Tokyo and then to Dubai. We want low-cost flights, budget hotels or hostels, cheap food spots, practical local transport, and a week-by-week itinerary that covers the main attractions without overspending. Keep the total budget limited and give a detailed split for flights, stays, food, city transport, visas, and sightseeing. save this trip in trip drafts after giving the plan and an average per=person split too for this trip', 'openai', 'A tight‑budget, 7‑day journey for four friends starting in Visakhapatnam, exploring Tokyo’s culture and food, then Dubai’s iconic sights, all while keeping travel, stay, food, and activities within a ₹350,000–₹400,000 budget. Flights are booked early for low fares, budget hostels and hotels are chosen, and local transport is optimized for cost and convenience.', 'Visakhapatnam', 'Tokyo, Dubai', 7, 4, 'friends', 350000.0, 400000.0, 'budget stay', 'flight + local cab', '["budget travel", "sightseeing", "food", "culture"]'::json, '7-day itinerary covering Tokyo and Dubai with low-cost options', '{"title": "7-Day Budget Adventure: Tokyo & Dubai from Vizag", "summary": "A tight\u2011budget, 7\u2011day journey for four friends starting in Visakhapatnam, exploring Tokyo\u2019s culture and food, then Dubai\u2019s iconic sights, all while keeping travel, stay, food, and activities within a \u20b9350,000\u2013\u20b9400,000 budget. Flights are booked early for low fares, budget hostels and hotels are chosen, and local transport is optimized for cost and convenience.", "source": "openai", "prompt": "Plan a 7 days budget trip for 4 friends starting from Visakhapatnam (Vizag), going first to Tokyo and then to Dubai. We want low-cost flights, budget hotels or hostels, cheap food spots, practical local transport, and a week-by-week itinerary that covers the main attractions without overspending. K